{"code":200,"message":"成功","flag":true,"data":{"prId":54702767,"scoringMethod":1,"name":null,"exerList":[{"exerID":4326103,"title":"恩格斯指出：“在历史上出现的一切社会关系和国家关系，一切宗教制度和法律制度，一切理论观点，只有理解了每一个与之相应的时代的物质生活条件，并且从这些物质条件中被引申出来的时候，才能理解。”这里的“物质生活条件”主要指（ ）","courseID":"H011901","catID":943793,"optNum":4,"a":"自然地理环境","b":"人口因素","c":"生产方式","d":"资源条件","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"C","keyType":"单选","analyze":"本题考查决定社会历史发展，决定社会关系、国家关系、宗教制度和法律制度的“物质生活条件”。四个选项中唯一具备决定性力量的因素只有“生产方式”，其他几个因素都只是对社会发展有重要的影响作用，起不到决定性作用。因此，选项C正确。选项A、B、D，所列举的三个因素都属于社会存在，即属于社会生活的物质方面，但是它们不具有决定性力量，只能对社会历史发展起影响作用，因此，并不能成为社会关系和社会制度的基础。故不选。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":26292,"correctTimesAmount":16577,"accuracyAmount":63.0,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":1,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["C"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","exerNum":null,"prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第五章 历史观的基本问题和人类社会社会的存在与发展"},{"exerID":4326104,"title":"历史唯物主义认为阶级社会发展的最终决定力量是（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943793,"optNum":4,"a":"国家政治权力","b":"天才人物的创造力","c":"社会生产","d":"阶级斗争","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"C","keyType":"单选","analyze":"社会发展的决定力量是物质生产方式。故C项